Class ScheduleTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • play.db.ebean.Model
      • models.ScheduleTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.avaje.ebean.bean.EntityBean, java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class ScheduleTemplate
extends play.db.ebean.Model
    This is a class for generating templates of schedules. All schedule templates have a title, learner type, id, and list of sessions within the template. Only admins can create schedule templates.
    Author:
    Julia Rapoport
